messages.speech:
That is actually very
                      interesting, because the more I was looking into
                      this particular fruit, the more respect I got for
                      it. And when I designed liver detox systems, we
                      have a special apple day, and we use malic acid
                      and apples as a preparation to dissolve
                      gallbladder and liver stones, and you can go on
                      and on and on about all the components of an
                      apple. It's so complicated, and yet so simple. You
                      just grab an apple, bite, chew, swallow, done.
